{"tid":938102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【笑對人生】14歲少女患罕見病臉部畸形，化身彩妝Youtuber活出自信！","createTime":"2018-12-12T04:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T01:41:32.000Z","uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4b864e04fb062a23c688b62c86936395f985dc96","tid":938102,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Nikki525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2FNikki525.jpg&h=87555a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國14歲少女Nikki Christou於年幼時確診「腦動靜脈血管畸形」（Arteriovenous malformation），自此右臉長出猶如腫瘤般的畸形外狀，不時被旁人嘲笑。雖然外表與常人不同，但她沒有掩飾這個缺陷，反而成為一名彩妝Youtuber，向觀眾傳達個人生活觀，活出自信！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/unnamed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Funnamed.jpg&h=7cea53d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChristou在6歲時便被醫院確診「腦動靜脈血管畸形」，因為左右臉部不平衡，她經常被問「是否因嚴重過敏致臉部畸形」，更有人曾跟她說「誰人打你？你太噁心了」。她在接受《每日電訊報》訪問時坦言，旁人的歧異目光令她相當難過，但她仍勇於接受自己外觀與別人不同，更不願掩飾自己真正的樣子，認為只有展示「真我」，才能活得有自信。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dop6JIlBtec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdop6JIlBtec&d=O5JMslzyeRwB2U9kY%2FOhh0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c7545de8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dop6JIlBtec</a><br />\nNikki自8歲起於YouTube 建立個人頻道，不時上載化妝教學、美食烘焙等短片，目前頻道已有逾50萬人訂閱。Nikki更曾與父親一起合作拍攝彩妝短片，由父親為她化妝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/24_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F24_600.jpg&h=a32925a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/12/06/article/85393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2Farticle%2F85393&d=O5JMslzyeRwB2U9kY%2FOhh0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=56596ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/12/06/article/85393</a>"},{"pid":"103b9e0246d02652594fd4b3d4ff375e6f70cd9c","tid":938102,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a0bb2c0468d3a32648da891ba06ee6f2d69d6a","tid":938102,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"本身靚到.."},{"pid":"53a44a286abc8ce638ef9c171413ff129218e44a","tid":938102,"uid":214258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"如果我有呢個病實頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人當異類真係好難受"},{"pid":"04cb52d0243d76eb0ad3e6f755f0c7ae3266ed8e","tid":938102,"uid":50253,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:45:07.000Z","msg":"試下遮住佢右邊<br />\n如果唔係個病應該幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863e8fb132880e322211ddf35970a41432ab8555","tid":938102,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個接受到<br />\n左邊幾靚女"},{"pid":"1b2f03e7df4aaefa190a3f3721f07fe4ed871f22","tid":938102,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73c14c0d6a3df06cbc92d9bb192f1cf1a6f15d2b","tid":938102,"uid":93986,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2f03e7df4aaefa190a3f3721f07fe4ed871f22","tid":938102,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪